Title: A geometrical interpretation of classical W-transformations

Authors: J.M. Figueroa-O'Farrill, E. Ramos, and S. Stanciu

Comments: 8 pages, Plain TeX, (the only changes are the Bonn preprint number

and a minor notational correction in the third section),BONN-HE-92-27,KUL-TF-92/34Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B297 (1992) 289-292

We give a simple geometrical interpretation of classical $\W$-transformationsas deformations of constant energy surfaces by canonical transformations on atwo-dimensional phase space.